    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skin on) into small, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potato</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potato is cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>outer</strong> <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces and shred the<strong> inner core[s]</strong></p><p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>into small, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the potato is golden, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong></p><p>Top with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, then return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 7-8 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> in a large bowl with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>creamy dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and <strong>shredded inner core</strong> to the bowl of dressing with the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/blt-salad-with-croutons/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your salad, add the <strong>roast</strong> <strong>potato</strong> to a bowl topped with the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>croutons</strong> and <strong>crispy bacon </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>BLT salad with croutons</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
